### FairFound Extension API Endpoints

### Get Available Categories
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/categories/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Marketplace Leaderboard (All)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/marketplace/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Marketplace Leaderboard (Filtered by Category)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/marketplace/?category=Mobile Developer
Content-Type: application/json

### Get FairFound Leaderboard (All)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/fairfound/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get FairFound Leaderboard (Filtered by Category)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/fairfound/?category=UI/UX Designer
Content-Type: application/json

### Compare Two Freelancers
POST http://localhost:8000/api/compare/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url1": "https://fairfound.com/freelancer/sarah-johnson",
    "url2": "https://fairfound.com/freelancer/michael-chen"
}

### List All Freelancers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/
Content-Type: application/json

### Search Freelancer Profiles (for comparison picker)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/profiles/?search=sarah
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Profiles (first 50)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leaderboard/profiles/
Content-Type: application/json
